"In the System Console, go to **Notifications > Email** and configure "
"Mattermost for your SMTP service. See the :ref:`SMTP configuration "
"<configure/environment-configuration-settings:smtp>` documentation for "
"details."
msgstr ""
"System Console에서 **Notifications > Email** 로 이동하여 SMTP 서비스에 맞게 Mattermost를 "
"구성하세요. 자세한 내용은 :ref:`SMTP configuration "
