#: ../../source/configure/smtp-email.rst:35
msgid "Set **Send Email Notifications** to **true**."
msgstr "**Send Email Notifications** 를 **true** 로 설정하세요."

#: ../../source/configure/smtp-email.rst:36
msgid ""
"Set the **Notification Display Name** for the account sending "
"notifications."
msgstr ""
"알림을 보내는 계정의 **Notification Display Name** 을 설정하세요."

#: ../../source/configure/smtp-email.rst:37
